# Number Guessing Game 🎮

A simple command-line game built using Python.

## Description
The computer randomly selects a number between 1 and 100. The player has 7 attempts to guess the correct number.

## Features
- Random number generation
- User input handling
- High/Low hints
- Limited attempts (7 turns)
- Win/Lose conditions

## Technologies Used
- Python
- Random Module
